[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man injured in microlight crash near Insch airfield

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been taken to hospital with potentially serious injuries after a microlight crash in Aberdeenshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened at about 11:15 at the Grampian Microlight and Flying Club.
The aircraft came down in a nearby field.
The man's injuries are not thought to be life-threatening.
